  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rogue Girl</h2>A roguelike game that will immerse you in an exciting adventure, where you will play as a beautiful devil girl called upon to fight an army of sinister zombies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=400 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skills</h2>Your path of progress depends on your decisions. As you level up, you will be offered random skills that allow you to mold your own unique play style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2>You will have to clear the gloomy rooms from the crowds of zombies. But be prepared, because with each room the danger and the number of enemies will only grow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Permanent Death</h2>Every action you take has consequences, and every death is the beginning of a new adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Roguelike elements: random rooms, enemies, skills, permanent death<br></li><li> Various types of enemies<br></li><li> Dozens of rooms<br></li><li> Dozens of skills (with buffs and debuffs<br></li><li> Detailed damage statistics (optional)<br></li><li> Dark fantasy-style graphics<br></li><li> Isometric camera<br></li><li> Atmospheric music</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rogue Girl</h2>A roguelike game that will immerse you in an exciting adventure, where you will play as a beautiful devil girl called upon to fight an army of sinister zombies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=400 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/9679d43b90b4e6ecf2161f7cd708baa0.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skills</h2>Your path of progress depends on your decisions. As you level up, you will be offered random skills that allow you to mold your own unique play style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/4c84e54a4aeeb2261f98d76c29ce292b.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2>You will have to clear the gloomy rooms from the crowds of zombies. But be prepared, because with each room the danger and the number of enemies will only grow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/b00dd586f2c854eda85913a4f2705f72.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Permanent Death</h2>Every action you take has consequences, and every death is the beginning of a new adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.poster.avif?t=1728887601\" width=398 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.webm?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877790/extras/02911f8d3d4f76a0030e317afdca44f2.mp4?t=1728887601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Roguelike elements: random rooms, enemies, skills, permanent death<br></li><li> Various types of enemies<br></li><li> Dozens of rooms<br></li><li> Dozens of skills (with buffs and debuffs<br></li><li> Detailed damage statistics (optional)<br></li><li> Dark fantasy-style graphics<br></li><li> Isometric camera<br></li><li> Atmospheric music</li></ul>",
